Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:24.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（童謠「龜與兔」  作詞：石原和三郎／作曲：納所弁次郎）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:07.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂　烏龜喲　烏龜先生喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:11.81,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上　沒有像你這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:16.49,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走得這麼慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:21.18,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會這麼慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  和和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  要去散步了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:00:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在咕噥什麼呢  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  和和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在為選什麼志願學校而煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  志願調查表還沒有交嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早就交了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是  我腦袋又不靈光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.93,0:01:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大學的事情也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…唯  這樣下去真的會變成NEET啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:18.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Not in Employment, Education or Training）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次說這話很沉重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就做NEET算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「NEET」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和最後第一志願填了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？  我填了國立學校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然感覺有點魯莽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想以那個目標努力衝刺一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也填那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太輕率了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為與和和在一起比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鬧什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  唯她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  你還沒決定志願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪填了什麼第一志願？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拿推薦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  你知道推薦是什麼意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬填了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我填了之前說的女子大學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  是名牌大學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也填那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬填的那個學校很難考嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  我正好帶著紅皮書  你要看嗎
