Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  英語！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好刺眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認清現實了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是日本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要英語！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們僅靠日語就能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校的英語考試不及格是會留級的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是入學考試的話  只要在別的學科上取得好成績就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  語文也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  傳給小律
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:05:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請選擇和下面的助動詞用法相同的一項
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西沒學過～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是一年級的範圍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助動詞可以通過歌來記住  以前沒學過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（以「龜與兔」曲調的助動詞記憶歌，歌詞為記憶大意）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:24.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癢癢的麻疹真想要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:31.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田園摩摩摩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跌啊踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:41.30,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小羊貝西真是認真
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:46.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這麼吵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:24.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,む ず む ず じ し む まし まほし～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:31.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,る ら ら る さーす りー りー りー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.32,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つ ぬ たり け り たし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,た し き けむ～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:41.30,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,らむ べし らし まじ なーり めりー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:46.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしてそんなり たり ごとし～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（現在開始比賽跑）（好  來比）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（在半途中休息）（趁現在）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:36.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（怎麼了）（其實是被欺負了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:39.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我來帶你去龍宮城）（那真是太感謝你了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（千年）（萬年）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是記得很清楚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就完全沒意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律填了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寫了未定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還完全不清楚將來的出路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那我也寫未定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑一張紙可決定不了我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年二班的田井中同學和平澤同學  馬上到辦公室來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…果然不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  你們先去活動室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦啊  和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪也是  彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯從小時候開始就完全沒變過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說已經進步不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律也是  認真幹的話是能幹好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯也是  集中力很強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個話題  到活動室裡繼續說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼紬會如此興奮呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:07:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才廣播裡叫的是唯學姐她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  總之是她們自作自受而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又幹了什麼錯事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…就是有點關於將來出路的問題要商談
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  請用  和和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  和是什麼時候認識唯的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從幼稚園開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼樣的邂逅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…沒什麼特別的契機…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不知不覺中就在我身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是本能地感覺到你是個可靠的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  你已經畫好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能舔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就是那樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  從那時開始就經常在同一個班級
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定有著不可思議的緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多傷腦筋的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說傷腦筋的話可能確實傷腦筋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學時  我們去野營
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽說要帶方便食品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像唯學姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來  還有在家政課上做章魚燒的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,材料是由大家帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  把章魚拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責章魚的唯忘了帶章魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果做了無章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有章魚也很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別的還有很多說都說不完的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一看到那無邪的笑容  就不知為何會原諒她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就那樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  剛才說過唯也已經進步不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得那大概是多虧了輕音社
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和真像大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  感覺像媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…母…母親！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的將來要好好考慮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯還沒決定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:10:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得還遠著呢  太難想像了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很遠的事了  一轉眼就到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和也上了年紀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來小佐和在高中時明明是那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會想成為老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  為什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  很難為情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想作參考  請一定要告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是因為當時喜歡的人說想成為老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說「那我也要做老師」…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動機不純啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢  和那個人怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但託了那個人的福才會進入大學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  重要的不是過去  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是現在啊  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  現在也沒有男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  唯  怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:11:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又知道了一件小佐和過去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  沒有被罵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～感覺人生真是各種各樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不會又搞出了什麼事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是  我是說人經歷了各種事情之後就會變得堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  志願調查表那樣行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼將來想做的職業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的職業嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  你覺得什麼比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己決定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學的時候不是說過想做幼稚園的老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是在發表題目為「將來的夢想」的作文的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將來的夢想是成為幼稚園的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成為幼稚園的老師之後  和小朋友們一直玩下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像唯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到發表作文  澪有一次獲得了優秀獎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  別說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想聽  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  我們來練習吧  練…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放棄吧  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學時候的澪是個很文靜很老實的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得一直都在看書
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是乎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時比現在還要害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  給我看看  給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個反應很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪畫畫也很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我經常逗她玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  100分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  我也想逗她玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是欺負嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學的時候不是會去逗自己喜歡的人玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛開始關係並不是特別好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的啊  被那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到這些事情之後就覺得焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把額頭伸過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的額頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是水性筆  放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  作文的發表怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…還記得？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼吧  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說給大家聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是三眼星人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:13:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小學四年級的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的作文獲得了縣級獎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得獎的人要在全校集會時在大家的面前朗讀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不想朗讀而沮喪著的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律來找我分擔煩惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不想讀作文  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很害羞啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好害羞的啊  你可厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一點也不厲害啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可班裡就澪一個人得獎啊  要是我的話就向大家炫耀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小律去得獎不就行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想在大家面前讀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:15:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪居然也能這麼大聲說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  現在去我家吧  來特訓！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別磨磨蹭蹭的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  有請四年一班學號1號的秋山澪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀不出來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  檯子低了點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再墊高點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是這個問題啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個拿下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這樣子  這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  紮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳梨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親告訴我  緊張的時候就把觀眾全部當作馬鈴薯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不會扮馬鈴薯  就扮個鳳梨～鳳梨給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…此後在人與人之間廣為流傳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完  四年一班  秋山澪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧律  讓我放鬆了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這故事真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律學姐之前是個好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然不像小律該當的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不知道怎麼誠心讚揚別人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  那作文發表進行的順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…澪寫的作文啦  內容很童話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癢癢癢癢癢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請諒解這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過自那之後就經常去律家裡玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  我教了你很多東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要改掉害羞的性格就要對自己自信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:17:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是說話的方式  句末裡加個「哦」的話就看起來自信滿滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是秋山澪  哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  就是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…還真是很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一想感覺你真沒教什麼正經的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不應該找律幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好過分啊  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯不是也這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不過還是要感謝她把我帶上音樂這條路…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪\N小澪\N澪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我說  現在不是聽我和律的故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於你們兩個的志願調查要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  總之先別想複雜的  大致考慮下自己想做什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那麼開個花店怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聽上去不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫平澤唯  是鎮上的花店老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種花難養嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:01.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（倒閉）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這需要植物相關的知識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  做個公司裡的OL怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是新人OL  今天也要遲到了  哎嘿～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的公司在隔壁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打擾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…要守時很困難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵你好過分…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公交導遊說不定不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  可以免費去各處旅遊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大家的公交導遊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家請看你們的右手邊  右手邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在右手邊有…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…容易暈車的人做不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  服務生怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個服務生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得記好多客人的菜單哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點心師呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是點心師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺會被自己吃掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就寫上自己現在最想做的怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己最想做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:21.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}第一希望　音樂家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明認真去寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告隊長  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂家…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我認真點寫！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是很認真的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太驚訝了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這是為了讓和和笑起來而進行的笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不  她覺得這是天方夜譚哦  唯同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂畢業了準備幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不出口…擔心姐姐  想和她去同一個地方這種話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我還沒有想過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  得好好想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…還沒想好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做個美容師  準備去考美容師的專業學校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去藝術大學吧  我想學攝影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有攝影這門課嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去外國語大學  然後去中國留學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去護士學校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家裡的酒坊幫忙
